videoSnippet.title: Take What You Can, Give Nothing Back || agadmator The Pirate
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Hello everyone. Here is a fun game I played against a strong opponent. Hope you enjoy it. Time controls are 1:30 + 30sec increment.

Marijan Belani vs Antonio Radić
Regional Croatia Cup, Cro; 2018-03-04
Grunfeld Defense: Burille, Vienna, Botvinik variation (D95)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. c4 Bg7 4. Nc3 d5 5. e3 O-O 6. Qb3 e6 7. Bd3 c5 8. cxd5 exd5 9. dxc5 Nc6 10. O-O Re8 11. Bb5 Bf5 12. Rd1 Be4 13. Nd4 Ng4 14. Nxe4 Nxd4 15. exd4 Rxe4 16. Be3 Qh4 17. h3 Rxe3 18. fxe3 Qf2+ 19. Kh1 Nxe3 20. Bf1 Nxd1 21. Rxd1 Bxd4 22. Bb5 Rd8 23. c6 bxc6 24. Bxc6 Kg7 25. Bxd5 Re8 26. Qd3 Re1+ 27. Rxe1 Qxe1+ 28. Kh2 Bg1+
